casebody.data:
STATE of North Carolina
v.
Alonzo Thomas WADE. No. 200P06-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 25, 2007. Alonza Wade, Pro Se. John G. Barnwell, Assistant Attorney General, C. Branson Vickory, III, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 15th day of December 2006 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Greene County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 25th day of January 2007."
